      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0041"/><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb92294">Hotel Tegetthoff</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb42213">I. Johannesgasse 23,
                  Wien</rs>.</hi></hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">XVIII. Spöttelga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 7</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0042"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Telegramme</hi></hi></seg><seg rend="right"><date when="1907-10-07">Montag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>früh</time>.</seg></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb92294">Tegetthoffhotel</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi>.</hi></seg></opener><p><salute>Lieber Freund,</salute> Darf ich vielleicht <date when="1907-10-08">morgen, Dien<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date>, <time>Abend</time> zu <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Euch</rs> kommen? Oder wollen wir uns vielleicht
               in der <rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb50">Stadt</rs> treffen? <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann</rs></hi> u. <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb26392">Leo Van-Jung</rs></hi> würden gern <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03253-1"/>mit dabei<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03253-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1907-10-08" subtype="Cf"/>.
               </note>. Ich bitte Dich um Nachricht ins <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb92294">Hotel Tegethoff</rs></hi> u. bin mit herzlichen Grüßen an Deine <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Frau</rs> u. Dich</p><closer>Dein <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
